messages.message:
Hi all, we've just merged a change to bump our go version from go 1.15 to go 1.18 within our main instabase repo. After rebasing / merging the latest changes, developers will need to upgrade their dev envs to go 1.18.1 (Intel - https://go.dev/dl/go1.18.1.darwin-amd64.pkg and M1 - https://go.dev/dl/go1.18.1.darwin-arm64.pkg).

If you identify any issues related to the go version bump, please discuss them in this message thread.
